Allure report
npm install -D allure-playwright allure-commandline
dir allure-results - To verify the result generated or not
npx allure generate allure-results --clean -o allure-report- command to generate report
npx allure open allure-report- To open report

Type Script
-> It is a programming language developed by microsoft
-> Improve version of javascript
-> Static typing language- we have to declare the data type of the variable.
    javascript: let age=25
    typescript: let age:number=25
-> Java script will allow any type of value to a variable, but in type script only allwoed data type value will be allowed.
-> let name:string="anu"
    console.log(name)
-> let ispassed:boolean=true
-> Error will check during compile time itself
-> File extension will be .ts instead of .js 
-> Code safety is more in typescript compare to javascript
-> npm install -g typescript: here -g means global, to use in all projects and all folders.
-> tsc -v : To check the version, here tsc is type script compiler.
-> tsc typescriptSample.ts : To compile the program 
-> node typescriptSample.js : To run the program, we have to convert to javascript then only browsers can iunderstand the program. Browsers cant understand typescript

await page.locator('.day:not(.old):not(.new)').filter({ hasText: /^8$/ }).click()

